The paper deals with problems at the intersection of language and vision, specifically visual question answering, which is a task in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, the paper also uses deep neural network models and external knowledge bases, which are common in sub-categories such as cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing, which is a common topic in cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
